sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Orchestrator<br/>saga state: STARTED
    participant S as Summarizer
    participant C as Classifier
    participant SW as Snowflake Adapter
    participant DB as Saga State Store

    Note over O,DB: Happy Path
    O->>DB: saga_id=X, step=SUMMARIZE, state=RUNNING
    O->>S: A2A POST /tasks {task_id, text}
    S-->>O: TaskResponse {summary, word_count}
    O->>DB: step=SUMMARIZE, state=DONE

    O->>DB: step=CLASSIFY, state=RUNNING
    O->>C: A2A POST /tasks {task_id, text}
    C-->>O: TaskResponse {tags}
    O->>DB: step=CLASSIFY, state=DONE

    O->>DB: step=SNOWFLAKE_WRITE, state=RUNNING
    O->>SW: A2A POST /tasks {task_id, enriched_article}
    SW-->>O: TaskResponse {status: failed, error: timeout}

    Note over O,DB: Compensation — reverse order
    O->>DB: saga_id=X, state=COMPENSATING
    O->>C: A2A POST /tasks/cancel {task_id}
    Note over C: mark output invalid
    C-->>O: cancelled

    O->>S: A2A POST /tasks/cancel {task_id}
    Note over S: mark output invalid
    S-->>O: cancelled

    O->>DB: saga_id=X, state=COMPENSATED
    Note over O: return failed TaskResponse to client
